  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "chapterTitle": "When You are Old",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25748206_33_430-1403",
          "range": "430-1403",
          "rangeStart": 430,
          "rangeEnd": 1403,
          "markText": "When you are old and grey and full of sleep,And nodding by the fire,take down this book,\nAnd slowly read,and dream of the soft look\nYour eyes had once,and of their shadows deep;\nHow many loved your moments of glad grace,\nAnd loved your beauty with love false or true,\nBut one man loved the pilgrim soul in you,\nAnd loved the sorrows of your changing face;\nAnd bending down beside the glowing bars,\nMurmur,a little sadly,how Love fled\nAnd paced upon the mountains overhead\nAnd hid his face amid a crowd of stars.\n",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1644811856,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-02-14 12:10:56",
          "chapterUid": 33,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=430&rangeEnd=1403",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=430&rangeEnd=1403"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_5_1415-1476",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1415-1476",
      "markText": "爱情，总说是在最好的年华里遇见最好的人。真正有几个能做到如杜拉斯说的那般：与你那时的面貌相比，我更爱你现在备受摧残的面容。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1415&rangeEnd=1476",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1415&rangeEnd=1476"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_5_592-733",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "592-733",
      "markText": "多少人爱你青春欢畅的时光， 爱慕你的美貌，或真情或假意， 唯有一人爱你那朝圣者的灵魂， 爱你哀戚的脸上岁月的痕迹；",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=733",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=592&rangeEnd=733"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_5_1505-1584",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1505-1584",
      "markText": "试想，当你年华老去、皱纹横生时身边还有一个与你厮守一生的爱人；当你走到暮年，还有人愿意俯下身来说“我爱你”。爱你，不为你那青春靓丽的年华，只爱你那美丽的灵魂。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1505&rangeEnd=1584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1505&rangeEnd=1584"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_3_1030-1063",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1030-1063",
      "markText": "这其中的哲理，只有在经历过体验过爱过痛过笑过流下泪之后，才能明白。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1030&rangeEnd=1063",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1030&rangeEnd=1063"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_15_1109-1153",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "1109-1153",
      "markText": "生命与文学不过是 一场英雄的梦。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1109&rangeEnd=1153",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1109&rangeEnd=1153"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_18_1017-1030",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1017-1030",
      "markText": "陷入爱情，永远都不必嫌早。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1017&rangeEnd=1030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1017&rangeEnd=1030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_6_645-759",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "645-759",
      "markText": "噢，亲爱的，别梦那消逝的流星的光彩， 也别梦那滴露中低垂的蓝星的残焰， 但愿我们是一对白鸟，飞翔在海波上，只有我和你",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=645&rangeEnd=759",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=645&rangeEnd=759"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_6_1300-1364",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1300-1364",
      "markText": "两人一次游历时，恰好有一对海鸥从头顶飞过，毛特向往地说：假如有来生，愿变做一只海鸥。几天后，毛特便收到叶芝寄给她的《白鸟》一诗。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1300&rangeEnd=1364",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1300&rangeEnd=1364"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_21_2081-2114",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2081-2114",
      "markText": "原来我们无须哀叹岁月的流逝，回首往事，我们都有生机勃勃的青春岁月。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2081&rangeEnd=2114",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2081&rangeEnd=2114"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_28_1462-1555",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1462-1555",
      "markText": "那伟大的女王，从海中跃出， 生来没父亲，她本可自主， 却挑了跛脚铁匠为夫。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1462&rangeEnd=1555",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1462&rangeEnd=1555"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_7_1057-1083",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1057-1083",
      "markText": "以其高度艺术化且洋溢着灵感的诗作表达了整个民族的灵魂",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1057&rangeEnd=1083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1057&rangeEnd=1083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_13_2415-2462",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "2415-2462",
      "markText": "叶芝才有了倾诉和创作的动力。毛特•冈晚年写给叶芝的信上说，“世人会因为她不嫁给他而感谢她的。”",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2415&rangeEnd=2462",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2415&rangeEnd=2462"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_28_4068-4140",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "4068-4140",
      "markText": "叶芝有着高傲而内省的性格，自视为社会精英。毛特·冈一直认为他太阴柔，与自己富有的刚烈气质完全不匹配。所以叶芝早期一直企图消减自己身上的女性气质。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4068&rangeEnd=4140",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4068&rangeEnd=4140"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_11_1657-1699",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1657-1699",
      "markText": "叶芝的诗受浪漫主义、唯美主义、神秘主义，以及象征主义和玄学诗的影响，形成其独特的风格",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1657&rangeEnd=1699",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1657&rangeEnd=1699"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_13_1803-1937",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1803-1937",
      "markText": "你是美丽的，我竭尽全力， 用古老而高尚的方式来爱你； 仿佛皆大欢喜，但我和你 却像那轮残月深感倦意。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1803&rangeEnd=1937",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1803&rangeEnd=1937"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_11_887-930",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "887-930",
      "markText": "好人总是快乐， 除非厄运临头，",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=887&rangeEnd=930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=887&rangeEnd=930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_13_1253-1268",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1253-1268",
      "markText": "亚当堕落后，没有不劳而获的事。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1253&rangeEnd=1268",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1253&rangeEnd=1268"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_8_983-1034",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "983-1034",
      "markText": "爱情不如灰暗的曙光和善， 希望也不如朝露可亲。",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=983&rangeEnd=1034",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=983&rangeEnd=1034"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_26_417-624",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "417-624",
      "markText": "因为你没有守住重誓， 旁的人成了我的朋友； 但第一次当我面对死亡， 或是梦中登上高处， 或是喝了点酒，心情振奋， 我会突然看见你的脸。",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=417&rangeEnd=624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=417&rangeEnd=624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25748206_3_678-696",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "678-696",
      "markText": "她嘱我把人生看淡，就像青草生于河堰。",
      "totalCount": 24,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25748206&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=678&rangeEnd=696",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b20327707188e2eeb20aab7?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=678&rangeEnd=696"
    }
